utions_by_ComplyPlus_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_1500x.jpg?v=1712318480 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Achieve_Excellence_with_Accredited_Health_and_Social_Care_Policy_Solutions_by_ComplyPlus_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_1000x.jpg?v=1712318480 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Achieve_Excellence_with_Accredited_Health_and_Social_Care_Policy_Solutions_by_ComplyPlus_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.jpg?v=1712318480 320w" width="2048" height="1152" alt="Achieve Excellence with Accredited Health and Social Care Policy Solutions by ComplyPlus™ - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Achieve Excellence with Accredited Health and Social Care Policy Solutions by ComplyPlus™ - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-kYHfwS QlfnY pf-154_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-155_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by DC_Studio Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-157_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The imperative for well-crafted health and social care policy has never been more pronounced. With the UK's ageing population, the rise of chronic illnesses, and the ever-increasing demand for services, the sector is under significant pressure. Effective policies ensure that care is delivered in a manner that is efficient, equitable, and responsive to the needs of diverse populations.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pVTFL cZzoXH pf-159_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hjGZqJ dfjDDX pf-160_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-jIkXHa bGnPis pf-161_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Wales_Care_Regulation_Standards_with_ComplyPlus_Solutions_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1712145319" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Wales_Care_Regulation_Standards_with_ComplyPlus_Solutions_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1712145319 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Wales_Care_Regulation_Standards_with_ComplyPlus_Solutions_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1712145319 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Wales_Care_Regulation_Standards_with_ComplyPlus_Solutions_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1712145319 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Wales_Care_Regulation_Standards_with_ComplyPlus_Solutions_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1712145319 320w" width="2149" height="1637" alt="Revolutionise Your Compliance with ComplyPlus™: The Leading Health and Social Care Policy Management System - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Revolutionise Your Compliance with ComplyPlus™: The Leading Health and Social Care Policy Management System - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-kYHfwS QlfnY pf-163_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-164_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by&nbsp;Rawpixel&nbsp;via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-166_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-167_ pf-text-1">The health and social care sector in the UK employs over 3 million people, making it one of the largest sectors in the economy.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-169_ pf-text-1">An estimated one in three people in the UK will benefit from social care services at some point in their life.</li></ul><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-171_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">These figures underscore the vast scope of health and social care services and the critical need for stringent policy frameworks to guide them.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pVTFL cZzoXH pf-173_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hjGZqJ dfjDDX pf-174_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-jIkXHa bGnPis pf-175_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key definitions</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Revolutionise_Your_Compliance_with_ComplyPlus_The_Leading_Health_and_Social_Care_Policy_Management_System_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1712318644" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Revolutionise_Your_Compliance_with_ComplyPlus_The_Leading_Health_and_Social_Care_Policy_Management_System_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1712318644 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Revolutionise_Your_Compliance_with_ComplyPlus_The_Leading_Health_and_Social_Care_Policy_Management_System_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_1500x.jpg?v=1712318644 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Revolutionise_Your_Compliance_with_ComplyPlus_The_Leading_Health_and_Social_Care_Policy_Management_System_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_1000x.jpg?v=1712318644 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Revolutionise_Your_Compliance_with_ComplyPlus_The_Leading_Health_and_Social_Care_Policy_Management_System_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.jpg?v=1712318644 320w" width="1667" height="1111" alt="Elevate Governance with ComplyPlus™: Advanced Health and Social Care Policy Compliance Solutions - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Elevate Governance with ComplyPlus™: Advanced Health and Social Care Policy Compliance Solutions - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-kYHfwS QlfnY pf-177_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-178_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by DragonImages

